e end of the journey; true success is a journey without an end. So many people relax after achieving something and they forget the undone. They neglect their untapped destiny and they halt their journey of life not reaching their real and true destination. Whilst we have life, we must live life. Whilst we have life, we must give a true meaning to life. Whilst we have life, we must dare to do the undone; though the road is weary; though we may be having a sense of fulfillment, and though we might have done something! Let us awake and pursue with all zeal and tenacity until we get to the real end of our true purpose and destiny, such that long after we are gone, the voice of our footprints will speak to inspire, build and raise a generation of champions !', 4606, 0), (86465, 'You are as the sun; the world is your stage; even without an audience, shine.', 5104, 0), (86466, 'In a world full of daisies dare to be a rose.', 5104, 0), (86467, 'When you look up and don’t see the stars, the universe may have cleared the sky for you to replace them.', 5104, 0), (86468, 'While the whole world was asleep, the caterpillar was awake, working towards becoming a butterfly.', 5104, 0), (86469, 'A rose does not answer its enemies with words, but with beauty.', 5104, 0), (86470, 'Don’t let mediocre people talk you out of your dreams', 18033, 0), (86471, 'If seeds despaired in their darkest hours, they would never rise to enjoy their brightest days.', 5104, 0), (86472, 'Change can be beautiful', 18034, 0), (86473, 'The universe sees your beauty', 18035, 0), (86474, 'Darkness is a prison from which only light escapes.', 5104, 0), (86475, 'Living honestly is a prerequisite for a clear conscience.', 3094, 0), (86476, 'Today’s storms usher in tomorrow’s sunshine.', 5104, 0), (86477, 'Honesty is a great thing, if tempered with love.', 12717, 0), (86478, 'say positive stay positive', 5489, 0), (86479, 'Hate is a parasite that will eat all compassion.', 18036, 0), (86480, 'I am but a man learning his way in this crazy life.', 18036, 0), (86481, 'They will turn you over, toss you about, fob you off, take you less seriously, because to get there, you must walk on your own feet.', 4168, 0), (86482, 'Live your best and leave the rest', 4168, 0), (86483, 'From all I learned about life, you can’t lose yourself in others to discover yourself. You will get lost forever.', 4168, 0), (86484, 'Sorry I''m late, I''m afraid I got lost on the path of life-Kakashi Sensei', 691, 0), (86485, 'When a rock transforms into a diamond, lesser stones will not speak of its beauty, but speak of its unpolishedness.', 5104, 0), (86486, 'Roses do not bloom hurriedly; for beauty, like any masterpiece, takes time to blossom.', 5104, 0), (86487, 'The larger the bricks your enemies throw at you the larger the palace you are going to build.', 5104, 0), (86488, 'To model the path of love, is to model the representation of God in your life.', 5129, 0), (86489, 'The happiest people in the world are those who give happiness to others.', 5104, 0), (86490, 'Sorry I''m late, I''m afraid I got lost on the path of life', 18037, 0), (86491, 'They ask little, for they know it is little they will receive for all their asking, but what little is so dear, as it always is to the autumn-hearted who know life is pitiful and infinitely sweet.', 18038, 0), (86492, 'Do you pray for our world or just your world? If all your prayers were answered, would it change our world or just your world?', 18039, 0), (86493, 'The road to Heaven is ascension', 18040, 0), (86494, 'Thou art but a feeble flower in the garden of the universe, yet thou hath a purpose much greater than thyself.', 15319, 0), (86495, 'Smile, just to infuriate those who envy you.', 5104, 0), (86496, 'In the bigger scheme of things, we are two pawns... waiting for life to make its move.#Fatalist', 10254, 0), (86497, 'Once upon a time, there was a world. It had three types of people in it. Those who walked a path of fear. Those who walked a path of faith and those who were lost. There were two realities; one that was visible to the senses and the other visible to the soul. Those on a path of fear, would see all things worldly. Those on a path of faith would feel the beauty. Those who were lost were incapable of neither seeing or feeling.', 18041, 0), (86498, 'This reality requires you to bury your nature and conform. This is the only way to survive. It is within this reality one often shares a minuscule of what one could share. Competition and scarcity dominate the mind and the heart shuts down. The lure with which one acquires is left with with subsequent hollowness. There was nothing to be had as all it was, was appearance. The conqueror leaves empty-handed. During a lonely moment, one can go and touch inside. It is here that the spirit shows how life is wasted by living a lie.', 18041, 0), (86499, 'And so in this reality, everything came unseen but perfectly felt. Here, everything shared possessed intensity. The vibrancy of energy moved from one good deed to another. Here one was bigger than his circumstances and here every interaction was multiplied. Here there was no work as every undertaking was a talented blessing.', 18041, 0), (86500, 'Your deepest scars tell the world of your greatest triumphs.', 5104, 0);
